1. *Dio* nam je dao veoma malo vremena da se pripremimo. (A part of us was given very little time to prepare.)
2. *Dio* cijele zgrade je zahvaćen vatrom. (A part of the whole building was engulfed in flames.)
3. Čini se da je *dio* problema riješen. (It seems that a part of the problem is solved.)
4. *Dio* puta je bilo vrlo teško. (A part of the journey was very difficult.)
5. *Dio* priče je potpuno izmišljen. (A part of the story is completely fabricated.)
6. *Dio* nje je zaboravio našu ljubav. (A part of her has forgotten our love.)